Welcome to my article! This artcle starts with "How we think about a solution". In other words, that is my thought process to solve the question. This article explains how I get to my solution instead of just posting solution codes or out of blue algorithms. I hope this aricle is helpful for someone.

# Intuition
Use two flags to check this is increasing or decreasing.

---

